snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Regicide iOS Trailer
snippet.description:
We're excited to reveal our trailer for Warhammer 40,000: Regicide - coming to the App Store on May 19th for $3.99 USD.

Follow us on social:
https://twitter.com/WH40kRegicide
https://www.facebook.com/WH40KRegicide/
https://www.twitch.tv/teamhammerfall

Buy Regicide on Steam now:
http://steamcommunity.com/app/322910/
